The saturday night WWX's party will be organised in a charming and luxury Parisian restaurant near <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/" target="_blank">Mozilla</a> headquarters, where the WWX2015 will take place. We’re talking about “Le Capitole” and you’ll find it at 105 Boulevard de Sébastopol, 75002 Paris.

<a href="https://www.silexlabs.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Image.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-204780 size-large" src="https://www.silexlabs.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Image-687x687.jpg" alt="Image" width="607" height="607" /></a>

&nbsp;



<a href="https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Le+Capitole/@48.866452,2.352206,15z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0xe63cd3171d07ff97" target="_blank">Googlemap link</a>

&nbsp;

The Haxe conference is full but you still can come to the party in order to meet the incredible people of the Haxe community (<a href="http://www.eventbrite.fr/e/billets-world-wide-haxe-conference-2015-16772484954?ref=ebtn">registration here</a>): on the agenda we find music, fresh beers and french wine at will and typical french cuisine: deli meat, croque-monsieur and boeuf bourguignon (<b><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beef_bourguignon" target="_blank">Beef bourguignon</a></b>). As last years, <a href="http://www.scengrafics.com/">Scengrafics</a> will light the night with projection of some old fashion video games or Haxe video.

